maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: The Art of the Laser Lasagne
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: L'art des Lasagnes Laser

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Good day, you two.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour, vous deux.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Pardon... Your name was \c[3]Albert\c[0], non?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Pardon... Ton nom c'est \c[3]Albert\c[0], non ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: That is correct.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est exact.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Uhm... may I ask what your class is?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Heu... Je peux demander quelle classe tu joues ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: That would be \c[3]Hexacast\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: La réponse serait un \c[3]Hexacast\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Ah! That is the \c[3]mage class\c[0], non?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah ! C'est la \c[3]classe des mages\c[0], non ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I don't know why...\. but you don't quite strike me as a mage, monsieur.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Je ne sais pas pourquoi...\. mais tu ne ressembles pas trop à un mage, monsieur.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: That's fine. I get that a lot.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est bon, je l'entends souvent.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I-Is that so...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: S-Si c'est bon...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well then... Good luck with the \c[3]Temple Mine\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon alors... Bonne chance dans le \c[3]Temple de la Mine\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: T-Thanks!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: M-Merci !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Uh...\. this guy's kinda hard to talk to, non?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Eh...\. Il est pas très causant, non ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Good day, Lea.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour, Lea.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hi!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Salut !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I must say, I appreciate your company.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Je dois dire, j'apprécie ta compagnie.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Not being so chatty, only saying what is necessary.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Tu jacasses pas trop. Tu dis seulement ce qui est nécessaire.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: It's nice for a change.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ça change un peu.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well then...\. Good luck with the \c[3]Temple Mine\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon alors...\. Bonne chance avec le \c[3]Temple de la Mine\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Good day. Back from the dungeon?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour. De retour du donjon ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Yes! We're ready to take that quiz, right Lea?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui ! On est prêt pour faire ce quiz, hein Lea ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Great! Good luck, then.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bien ! Bonne chance, alors.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hi!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Salut !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Good day, Lea. It's great to see you back in CrossWorlds again.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour, Lea. C'est bien de te revoir dans CrossWorlds.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hello, Albert!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour, Albert !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Good day, Toby.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour, Toby.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Right, you're playing together now.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah oui, vous jouez ensemble maintenant.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: That's good. Hexacasts shine the most when in a party.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est bien. Les Hexacasts sont meilleurs quand ils sont dans un groupe.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: That's true. Now that you mention it, I should probably learn a few more buff and debuff skills.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est vrai. Maintenant que tu le mentionnes, je devrais peut-être apprendre quelques circuits de buff et debuff.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Good idea, those are very useful indeed.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonne idée, ils sont effectivement très utiles.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Actually... I have a lot more questions about this class. You seem very experienced, so if you don't mind me asking...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: En fait... J'ai d'autres questions à propos de cette classe. Tu sembles avoir plus d'expérience que moi, donc si ça ne te dérange pas...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh bother... Maybe another time.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah, non... Peut-être une autre fois.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: You're still early in the game, anyway. Not too much you can do wrong now.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Tu es encore assez tôt dans le jeu de toute façon. Tu ne peux pas tellement te tromper maintenant.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I-I see! Okeydokey!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: J-Je vois ! Dacodac !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hello, my dears! Please make yourself at home and let me know if you need anything.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour, mes chéries ! Faites comme chez vous et dites-moi si vous avez besoin de quelque chose.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Lin, I was wondering...\. are you the leader of this guild?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Lin, je me demandais...\. si tu étais la cheffe de la guilde ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well, yes... you could say that.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bien, oui... on peut dire ça.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I started this guild together with \c[3]Al\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: J'ai démarré cette guilde avec \c[3]Al\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: But we're all pretty much family at this point!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais on est tout un peu comme une famille ici.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: It sure feels like visiting a family house.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est sûr, on a l'impression d'être dans une maison en arrivant ici.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: With so many grown up children...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Avec tant d'enfants adultes...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Why yes, we all just stayed young at heart!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui c'est ça, on est tous resté jeunes dans nos cœurs !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Life is too short to be all serious business, eh?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: La vie est trop courte pour être prise trop sérieusement, non ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oui!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Lea, dear, you're all by yourself right now?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Lea, ma chérie, tu es toute seule maintenant ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well, just tell me when you two completed the \c[3]Temple Mine\c[0] so we can have the quiz!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon, alors dis-moi juste quand vous deux vous aurez terminé le \c[3]Temple de la Mine\c[0] pour qu'on puisse démarrer le quiz !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Ah don't worry, my dear! I'm sure you'll do great!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah ne t'inquiète pas. Je suis sûre que tu vas réussir !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Lin, the newbies are here!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Lin, les newbies sont là !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Now, now, Raphael - don't call them 'newbies'! It's rude.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Non, non, Raphael ! Ne les traite pas de "newbies" ! C'est méchant.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Come on, Chief! You know I'm joking.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh, aller, Cheffe ! Tu sais que je blague.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: My, look at you two!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah, mais qu'est-ce qu'on a là ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Welcome to our humble headquarters!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bienvenue dans notre modeste quartier général !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: My nickname is \c[3]Hlin\c[0], but you can call me \c[3]Linda\c[0] or just \c[3]Lin\c[0]!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mon pseudo est \c[3]Hlin\c[0], mais vous pouvez m'appeler \c[3]Linda\c[0] ou juste \c[3]Lin\c[0] !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: And this is \c[3]Albert\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Et lui c'est \c[3]Albert\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Good day. Pleased to meet you.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour. Ravi de vous rencontrer.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Bonjour!\. I am Emilie!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour !\. Je suis Emilie !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hi, Lea!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Salut, Lea !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: A \c[3]Pentafist\c[0] and \c[3]Spheromancer\c[0]! Oh, how wonderful!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Un \c[3]Pentafist\c[0] et un \c[3]Spheromancer\c[0] ! Ah, c'est fantastique !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: If you two joined our guild, we'd have members of all 5 classes!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Si vous deux vous rejoignez notre guilde, on aura des membres de chacune des 5 classes !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Ah, but I'm getting ahead of myself.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais bon, je suis encore allée un peu trop vite.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Let's go somewhere comfortable.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Allons dans un endroit un peu plus confortable.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Such a cozy, little house!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est une maison si mignonne ici !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Nothing like I had imagined it.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Je l'aurais pas imaginée comme ça.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Thank you so much!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Merci beaucoup !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: It's like the house I always wanted to own.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est effectivement la maison que j'ai toujours rêvé d'avoir.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Now of course it's not the fortress that many people expect.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bien sûr, ce n'est pas la forteresse auquel certaines personnes s'attendent.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: But really, the few of us wouldn't know what to do with all the space, eh?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais au fond : on est pas si nombreux que ça. On aurait fait quoi avec toute la place qu'on a ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Japp. Also it's not like we could afford the castle of our dreams.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Japp. De toute façon, c'est pas comme si on pouvait se permettre d'avoir le château de nos rêves.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Yes, yes!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui, oui !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: So...\. there're just...\. 4 members right now?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Donc...\. il y a juste...\. 4 membres en ce moment ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Not quite, dear. Someone else joined us not too long ago, but he isn't around at the moment.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Pas vraiment, ma chérie. Quelqu'un d'autre nous a rejoints il y a pas longtemps, mais là il est hors-ligne.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: So that makes \c[3]5 members\c[0] in total.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Donc ça fait \c[3]5 membres\c[0] au total.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: And you two just started playing, right?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Et vous deux vous venez juste de commencer à jouer, c'est ça ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oui! We just reached Bergen and were about to enter the mine.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui ! On vient d'arriver à Bergen et on allait entrer dans la mine.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Ah, wonderful! The first real dungeon. It's always something special.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah, formidable ! Le premier vrai donjon. C'est toujours quelque chose d'un peu spécial.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: It's the first time you'll be entering a \c[3]heritage site of the Ancients\c[0]!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est la première fois que vous entrerez dans un \c[3]patrimoine culturel des Anciens\c[0] !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh? What is that?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh ? Qu'est-ce que c'est ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Why, it's what we \c[3]Seekers\c[0] are looking for.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh, c'est ce que nous les \c[3]\v[lore.title.seeker]s\c[0] cherchons.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: We try to solve the \c[3]Secret of the Ancients\c[0], eh?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Nous essayons de résoudre le \c[3]Secret des Anciens\c[0], non ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Each heritage site includes a few pieces of the big puzzle.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Chaque lieu héberge une partie du grand puzzle.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oui, oui! The plot.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui, oui ! L'intrigue !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: That's right, dear!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est ça, chérie !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Did you know that the full secret of the Ancients has yet to be discovered?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Tu savais que le secret entier des Anciens n'a toujours pas été découvert ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Really?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Vraiment ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh yes, they're so crafty about it!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh oui, Ils restent toujours aussi évasifs là-dessus !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: The official path of the game will only tell you so much.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Le chemin officiel du jeu ne nous en dit pas tellement beaucoup.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: They keep releasing new quests that will reward you with more information.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ils continuent de sortir quelques nouvelles quêtes de temps en temps, qui donnent un peu plus d'information à chaque fois.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: But the puzzle has yet to be completed!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais le puzzle entier n'a pas encore été résolu !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: And yes, that is what our guild is all about.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Et oui, c'est pour ça que notre guilde existe.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: We are the First Scholars and we study the Ancients!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Nous sommes les Premiers Érudits et nous étudions les Anciens !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: We want to be the first to unravel the secret!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Nous voulons être les premiers à découvrir le secret !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Ah! I see.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah ! Je vois.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: And now you understand why our guild is so small!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Et maintenant vous comprenez pourquoi notre guilde est si petite.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Nyeeahahahahahaha!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Nyeeahahahahahaha !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hush, Raphael!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Chut, Raphael !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well, I think it's nice to be in a small guild like this.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Moi je trouve ça bien d'être dans une petite guilde comme celle-là.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: There is just too much stress and responsibility with the big ones.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Dans les grosses, il y a toujours beaucoup de stress et de responsabilités.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I think it's nice, right Lea?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Moi je trouve ça bien. Hein, Lea ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Lea, my dear, you've been so quiet all the time. Is something the matter?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Lea, ma chérie, tu es bien silencieuse depuis le début. Quelque chose ne va pas ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: [shakes head]
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh, she is just shy.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh, elle est juste timide.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Also she just \c[1]kills everything with a single-hit\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah, sinon, elle \c[1]tue tout en un seul coup\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: But she's also \c[3]way over-leveled\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais elle a aussi un \c[3]niveau bien trop élevé\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: So it's pretty chill to go around and bash enemies with her.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Donc c'est assez tranquille de se balader et de chasser avec elle.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Nyeeahahahahahaha!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Nyeeahahahahahaha !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Wait, what?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Attends, quoi ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Anyway, I'd be glad to join! You too, Lea?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: En tout cas, moi je vous rejoindrai bien ! Toi aussi, Lea ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: So, where do we sign?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Donc, où est-ce qu'on signe ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Now, now! We have a small tradition here for new members.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Du calme, du calme ! Nous avons une petite tradition pour les nouveaux membres.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: A \c[3]quiz\c[0]!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Un \c[3]quiz\c[0] !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: ...A quiz?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: ... Un quiz ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh don't worry, it's very simple!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh, ne t'inquiète pas, c'est très simple !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: We want to test your knowledge of the Ancients.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: On veut juste tester vos connaissances sur les Anciens.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: But for that I'm afraid you first need to complete the Temple Mine in Bergen!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais pour ça, vous devez d'abord terminer le Temple de la Mine à Bergen !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Just make sure to read everything at the heritage site and you should be well prepared.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Il faut juste que vous lisiez tout sur le lieu culturel et vous devriez être prêt pour le quiz.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: D'accord! Sounds good to me.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: D'accord ! Moi ça me va !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Come on, Lea! Let's do the dungeeeeon!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Allez, Lea ! Allons faire le donjooooon !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: That's the spirit!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Voilà ! C'est ça l'esprit !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: It was a pleasure to meet you two.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'était un plaisir de vous rencontrer, vous deux.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Feel free to drop by whenever you like.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Vous êtes libres de revenir quand vous voulez.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh, and I suppose now is a good time to share contacts, too!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah, avant que j'oublie : Si on s'échangeait nos contacts !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: First Scholar Members
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Membres des Premiers Érudits

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Alrighty! Tell me when you're ready for the quiz!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est bon ! Dites-moi lorsque vous serez prêtes pour le quiz !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Enter the \c[3]Temple Mine\c[0] together with \c[3]Emilie\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Entrez dans le \c[3]Temple de la Mine\c[0] avec \c[3]Emilie\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Contact other players
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Contacter d'autres joueurs

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Learn how to contact other players of CrossWorlds.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Apprenez à contacter d'autres joueurs dans CrossWorlds.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: You find your contacts in the \c[3]second tab\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Vous trouverez vos contacts dans le \c[3]deuxième onglet\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: You can \c[3]contact\c[0] those players to have a small chat as long as they are \c[3]online\c[0].
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Vous pouvez \c[3]contacter\c[0] ces joueurs pour démarrer une petite discussion, tant qu'ils sont \c[3]en ligne\c[0].

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Repeat?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Répéter ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Yes
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: No
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Non

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: So you two are determined to enter the dungeon together?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Donc vous voulez absolument faire le donjon à deux ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: You bet we are!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bien sûr qu'on veut !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: You are aware that dungeons are instanced, right?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Vous savez que les donjons sont instanciés, non ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: You have to beat it by yourselves.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ça veut dire que vous devez le faire chacun de votre côté.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oui, oui! We know.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui, oui ! On sait !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: But we enter at the same time and do a race on who completes the dungeon first.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais on entre en même temps et on fait la course à celle qui finira le donjon en premier.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Just like with \c[3]Rhombus Dungeon\c[0]. I was first that time.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Comme pour le \c[3]Donjon de Rhombus\c[0]. Là c'était moi la première.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well, to be honest, it was very close.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon, pour être honnête, c'était très tendu.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh Junge, you're quite the competitive pair!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh, Junge... Vous aimez bien la compétition, vous deux !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hello Lea, how are you doing? Emilie not with you right now?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour Lea, comment ça va ? Emilie n'est pas avec toi ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hi!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Salut !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Japp. You're a quiet one, alright.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Japp. Tu es assez du genre silencieuse.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well, not that you'd get to talk much with chatty Emilie being around.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon, non pas que tu puisses beaucoup en placer une, lorsque cette pipelette d'Emilie est avec toi.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Holerö! Did you finish the dungeon?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Holerö ! Vous avez fini le donjon ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oui, we're ready for the quiz now!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui, on est prêt pour le quiz maintenant !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: So, who won the race?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Donc, qui a gagné la course ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Ah...\. Lea did.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah...\. Lea.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh, congratulations Lea!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh ! Félicitations, Lea !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh well...\. all those stupid cold bugs put me off.\. I really hate bugs, you know?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ah...\. Tous ces insectes froids stupides m'ont ralentie.\. Je peux vraiment pas sentir ces insectes, tu comprends ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Yes, of course.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui, bien sûr.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I was victorious, once again!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Moi ! Encore une fois !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Don't worry Lea, there are still several dungeons left.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ne t'inquiète pas, Lea, il reste encore pas mal de donjons.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Right and I'll win all of them!!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui et je vais tous les gagner !!

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: [shakes head]
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Whoa, this rivalry right there.\. Scary.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ouah, cette rivalité...\. C'est...\. effrayant.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Forgotten Lines of Yore
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Lignes oubliées de Yore

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: The new Meta
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Le nouveau Méta

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Story of the Ancients
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Histoire des Anciens

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Bonjour everyone, look who's back again!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bonjour tout le monde. Regardez qui est revenue !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Hi...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Salut...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Lea, dear!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Lea, chérie !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: It's good to see you again after all this time.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est bon de te revoir après si longtemps.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Our little runaway has returned!\. Hi!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Notre petite fugueuse est revenue !\. Salut !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Welcome back.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Rebonjour.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: We've been very worried about you. It has been so long...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: On était vraiment inquiète pour toi. Ça faisait si longtemps...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Sorry...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Désolé...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Dear, what exactly happened to you back then?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Chérie, qu'est-ce qui s'est passée exactement ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well...\. we couldn't really figure out the details.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon...\. Savoir ce qui s'est passé, c'est difficile à dire.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: But it's clear that none of it was Lea's intention.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais une chose est claire : ce n'était pas son intention de partir.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Why of course not!\. There never was any doubt about that.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bien sûr que non !\. Il n'y a jamais eu aucun doute là-dessus.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well...\. There really wasn't.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon...\. Il y en avait vraiment pas.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I was just stubborn.\. I'm sorry, Lea.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: J'étais juste têtue. Je suis désolée, Lea.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: It's alright, Emilie. We've all been rather bummed out about the raid.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'est bon, Emilie. On a tous été plutôt déçus à cause du raid.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: But I'm sure that another opportunity will come up, soon enough!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mais je suis sûr qu'on aura bientôt une nouvelle opportunité pour un autre !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: So that's all well and great, but one major question remains.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon, tout ça c'est bien et tout, mais il reste une question majeure.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: What about the \c[3]hugging of Lukas\c[0]?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: C'était pour faire quoi le \c[3]câlin avec Lukas\c[0] ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Nyeeahahahahahaha!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Nyeeahahahahahaha !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Sorry...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Désolé...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Whoa...\. I'm joking, just joking!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Hé...\. C'était une blague, juste une blague !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Why make a big deal out of it? Maybe she just likes to hug people...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Pourquoi est-ce que c'est si important ? Peut-être qu'elle aime juste faire des câlins aux gens...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.note: ou ptet que t'aime bien détourner l'attention...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: It really did come out of nowhere, though...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Ça venait vraiment de nulle part, par contre...
Oh, j'aurais bien voulu voir ça.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Man, I wish I could have seen that.
Hm...
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Mmm...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I'd rather like to know how this whole situation was even possible to begin with.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: J'aimerais plutôt savoir, comment tout cela à bien pu arriver.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Lea being online with no way to contact her.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Lea était en ligne, mais aucun moyen de la contacter.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Especially over such a long time.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Surtout pendant aussi longtemps.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Yeah, it is really strange.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui, c'est vraiment étrange.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: You know what? You should talk to Ivan about this!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Tu sais quoi ? Tu devrais en parler avec Ivan !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Please, that's not how it works.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Non, c'est pas comme ça que ça marche.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Why would he care about individual user issues like this?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Qu'est-ce qu'il en aurait à faire de quelques problèmes individuels comme ça ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: All games have them. It's not relevant for the bigger picture.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Tous les jeux en ont. Pour une vision globale, ça ne fait aucune différence.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Yeah, yeah...\. as long as profits are flowing, the big-shot shareholder is happy!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui, oui...\. Tant que l'argent coule à flot, Monsieur le grand actionnaire est content !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Nyeeahahahahahaha!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Nyeeahahahahahaha !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Just for the record, that's why I'd never introduce you to him.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Juste pour que tu saches : c'est pour ça que je ne te le présenterai jamais.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Well...\. Sorry, but I have to logout now.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bon...\. Désolé, mais il faut que je me déconnecte.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: I'll be back tomorrow so we can continue our dungeon race then!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Je serais de retour demain, pour que l'on puisse continuer notre course au donjon !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oui, same for me!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oui, pareil pour moi !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: See you again tomorrow!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: On se voit demain !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Bye!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bye !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Déconnexion

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Déconnexion

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Hm...\. Un actionnaire qui s'appelle Ivan ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Bye.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bye.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Who was he talking about?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: De qui est-ce qu'il parlait ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Sorry?
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Désolé ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Hein ?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Bye!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Bye !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh! Yes, of course! Until tomorrow, Lea!
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Oh ! Oui, bien entendu ! À demain, Lea !

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Déconnexion

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Tu as vu quelque...

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Oh, so you remembered something?

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: Gautham... he didn't look like he was an avatar.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Gautham... Il n'avait pas l'air d'être un avatar.

maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.orig: He was the spitting image of how I remember him from real life.
maps/autumn/guild/inner-fs-og.json/entit.text: Il était exactement comme ce dont je me souvenais de lui dans la vie réelle.
